snippet.title: Karmaflow Update: Simone, Mark and Coen from Epica
snippet.description:
Karmaflow: The Rock Opera Videogame

Simone, Mark and Coen from Epica recently recorded their parts for Karmaflow: The Rock Opera Videogame!

Get your copy of the (physical and digital) Soundtrack here:
https://karmaflow.bandcamp.com

Get your copy of KARMAFLOW: THE ROCK OPERA VIDEOGAME on Steam here (only EUR 4.99!):
http://store.steampowered.com/app/317940/

http://www.karmaflowgame.com
http://www.facebook.com/karmaflowgame.com
http://www.twitter.com/karmaflowgame
http://www.basecampgames.com/
